 }}</ref>他們在2020年1月成為美國公民。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.yahoo.com/entertainment/robbie-amell-italia-ricci-become-204319409.html |title = Robbie Amell and Italia Ricci Become United States Citizens: 'Today Was Awesome' |author = Natalie Stone |date = 2020-01-24 |publisher = yahoo |language = en |access-date = 2021-01-26 |archive-date = 2021-01-31 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210131143805/https://www.yahoo.com/entertainment/robbie-amell-italia-ricci-become-204319409.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>

